title: Marvel NOW! Week 60/All-New Marvel NOW! Week 3 01/08/2014
description:
Hi folks! As per usual, I didn't see a collected torrent for this week's Marvel NOW! titles yet, so I thought I'd upload one. Included are:

A+X 016
All-New Marvel NOW! Point One 001
All-New X-Factor 001
Avengers A.I. 008.NOW
Avengers World 001
Black Widow 001
Cable and X-Force 018
Daredevil - Dark Nights 008 (of 8)
Deadpool 022
Infinity Heist 004 (of 4)
Inhumanity Awakening 002 (of 2)
Iron Man 020
Savage Wolverine 014.NOW
Wolverine 013
Young Avengers 015 


It's the final issue for Young Avengers! It was a great run while it lasted, and at least it's wrapping up while it's still a great title.

I originally included Revolutionary War: Alpha in the torrent, but then checked with Brevoort on twitter-- it's not, in fact, part of either Marvel NOW! or All-New Marvel NOW! so I had to scrap that. Sad-- but you should still check it out, it's a good read.

If you like them and have the money, BUY THEM and support your favorite creators, writers, artists, local comic shops and publishers. All my thanks to all the uploaders and scanners and seeders out there! Enjoy! (and seed!)

Seriously, buy these comics.
